all they had. The only thing, they were Air City 
Rescue. That's all we did. We practiced Air City

06:04.181 --> 06:04.922
Rescue mission.

06:07.990 --> 06:13.538
with that part of the Portuguese Air Force. And 
did, I mean, were you ever called in to help them as

06:13.558 --> 06:18.405
far as RC rescue? No.

06:26.155 --> 06:35.128
How were the relations between your men in general 
on these, or your airmen and your officers and the

06:26.155 --> 06:35.128
Portuguese that lived in that area?

06:38.922 --> 06:47.112
There was no tension at all.

06:47.132 --> 06:54.802
The presence of the base there meant a lot to the 
economy of that island.

06:54.822 --> 07:03.293
It's called the Isle of Tessera, which means the 
Third Island, and it was a third great island.

